                    "company": "Utrecht University",
                    "description": "USBO studies public issues and public organizations in their interaction with the developments in politics and society. The key question in this is how public organizations and private organizations with a public task deal with current social issues, how they shape their public responsibilities and deliver public value. I established a sport consultancy department within USBO. My own advice and contract research focuses on governance, organization and management issues in sport organizations, such as good governance, CSR and legacy of mega sport events. Some of my contractors are KNVB, PSV, FC Utrecht, NOC*NSF, Ministry of Health, Welfare and Sport, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, Johan Cruyff Foundation. \n\nhttps://www.uu.nl/organisatie/departement-bestuurs-en-organisatiewetenschap",
                    "title": "Senior consultant USBO Advies",
                    "employment_type": null
                },
