                        }
                    },
                    "company": "Utrecht University",
                    "description": "The research focus area Sport & Society is working on an integrated approach to scientific and social questions about sports in relation to issues of health, inclusion and security. It is linking academic excellence and fundamental research to a social mission. I coordinate the interdisciplinary collaboration between six faculties and develop a joint research and education programme. Also, I enhance the international profile of sport research at Utrecht University, including raising research funds (NWO, ZonMW, EU) and valorization. Besides this, I supervise Sport & Society research on  good governance and integrity.\n\nwww.uu.nl/sportandsociety",
                    "title": "Coordinator research focus area 'Sport & Society'",
